WEBVTT

00:00:00.970 --> 00:00:03.960
Every witness believes they remember what happened.

00:00:04.430 --> 00:00:05.650
Most of them are certain.

00:00:06.440 --> 00:00:08.260
But memory isn't a recording.

00:00:08.830 --> 00:00:10.030
It's a reconstruction.

00:00:10.820 --> 00:00:12.380
Every detail matters.

00:00:12.790 --> 00:00:14.160
Every glance counts.

00:00:14.830 --> 00:00:17.660
Every decision begins with observation.

00:00:29.820 --> 00:00:30.320
You have…

00:00:30.830 --> 00:00:31.740
two seconds.

00:00:32.750 --> 00:00:33.700
What changed?

00:00:41.750 --> 00:00:44.520
Play Two Second Witness now on Android.
